snippet.title: Elder Kings 2 - Release & Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the EK2 Discord: https://discord.gg/elderkings
Check out EK2's website: https://elderkings.com/

Elder Kings 2 is a fan-made total conversion mod for Crusader Kings 3, based on the popular Elder Scrolls series and the Elder Scrolls Online MMO. From Yokuda to Morrowind, from Skyrim to Elsweyr, choose any feudal ruler to steer your dynasty through the turmoil of the Interregnum, a time without a Dragonborn Emperor on the Ruby Throne, starting from either 2E 440 or 2E 450.
Release: 11/11/22

This is a project by fans, for fans. It is a fan mod created for Crusader Kings 3 and has no affiliation with Bethesda.

This trailer first premiered at ModCon 2, a modding convention by modders of the PDS games Crusader Kings 3 and Imperator: Rome.
You can watch the entire EK2 panel here: https://youtu.be/FbE4wCfbvbQ?t=18611

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Script -- the worm(hashtag)3183 (Discord) & AJ
Voice Acting -- Verrix(hashtag)2785 (Discord)
Scoring -- Will_PA - soundcloud.com/willp-a
Recording -- AJ & Theyn
Editing -- Castox
Produced -- AJ & Theyn
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
